Interface IAttributeMap<K,V>

  • Type Parameters:
    K - The type of attribute key.
    V - The type of attribute value.

    public interface IAttributeMap<K,V>
    Implemented by classes that support attribute maps. Implementers need only implement the getAttributes method. All other methods have default implementations.

    • Method Summary
